thread.title: Jayne Stinton
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by Jayne Stinton

author: Jayne Stinton
title: Jayne Stinton
text: Once staff arrived fabulous service, unfortunately I had booked late in the day and the counter staff member was outside in car lot and did not know I was there to pick up car. The phone number on counter only rang the counter telephone, needless to say I was pretty annoyed. Staff were apologetic and very helpful. Just a little hiccup!
